headline.print_headline: Delta Jet Returns to Jamaica After Fluid Leak
headline.main: Delta Jet Returns to Jamaica After Fluid Leak

lead_paragraph: A Delta Airlines jet was forced to return to the airport in Jamaica shortly after takeoff Monday because of an apparent mechanical problem in one of its engines, the company said.
